00:00:00.460 --> 00:00:04.330
As far as transitions are concerned, there's a transition goes from a source

00:00:04.330 --> 00:00:09.680
state, goes to a target state. The transition can be labeled with some

00:00:09.680 --> 00:00:15.120
kind of triggering event. There can be a guard on it. There can be an action.

00:00:16.219 --> 00:00:20.990
Okay, that takes place when the transition occurs. And as we've

00:00:20.990 --> 00:00:25.670
noticed there can be forks in the transition arcs, and there can even be joins.

